@angus-c are namespaced events totally out of the question for Flight? I could see namespaced events offering quite a few benefits in regards to scoping, semantics, and flexibility in reacting to the pulse of the application.

For example:

``` javascript
// Potentially a routing component or some other overseeing component
this.on('transition.*', function() {
  // Prepare for a page transition
})


// A smaller component that needs to act on a specific transition
this.on('transition.profile', function(){
  // Set up profile page and attach to dom
})


// The communication component
this.trigger('transition.profile', profileInfo)
```
